OL,3,CBridget Jones statue becomes permanent
OL,4,Cfixture on Leicester Square trail
OL,6,FA statue of Bridget Jones will remain
OL,7,Fa permanent fixture on a trail of
OL,8,FBritain's best-loved characters in
OL,9,Fcentral London.The announcement comes
OL,10,Fas the first film in the franchise of
OL,11,Fthe same name celebrates its 25th
OL,12,Fanniversary.
OL,14,FThe figure was unveiled at Leicester
OL,15,FSquare's Scenes in the Square trail in
OL,16,FNovember last year, with actress Renee
OL,17,FZellweger saying at the time that her
OL,18,Frole as the protagonist had been a
OL,19,F"pretty big blessing".
OL,26,@{D@AOU{D@UO]
