OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1776423773
OL,3,CBridget Jones statue becomes permanent
OL,4,Cfixture on Leicester Square trail
OL,6,FThe trail features statues of movie
OL,7,Fcharacters such as Harry Potter,
OL,8,FBatman, Paddington, Wonder Woman and
OL,9,FMary Poppins in the capital's film
OL,10,Fcentre.
OL,12,FKirsty Tullett-Jones, director of
OL,13,Fmarketing and communications for
OL,14,FDiscover Leicester Square, said the
OL,15,FBridget Jones statue becoming a
OL,16,Fpermanent feature "cements" the
OL,17,Fcharacter in cultural history.
OL,19,FShe said: "For 25 years, Bridget has
OL,20,Fmade Londoners laugh, cry and feel
OL,21,Fseen.
OL,26,@xD@SOUxD@[O]{D@KOU
