OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1776423773
OL,3,CBridget Jones statue becomes permanent
OL,4,Cfixture on Leicester Square trail
OL,6,F"The reaction to her arrival in
OL,7,FLeicester Square has been incredible,
OL,8,Fshowing just how much she continues to
OL,9,Fresonate with audiences today.
OL,11,F"With the trail already celebrating
OL,12,Fthe very best of film, it felt only
OL,13,Fright to honour one of the most iconic
OL,14,From-com characters of all time. Making
OL,15,FBridget a permanent fixture cements
OL,16,Fher place in both Leicester Square and
OL,17,FBritish cultural history."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUyD@ZO]
