OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1776423773
OL,3,CBridget Jones statue becomes permanent
OL,4,Cfixture on Leicester Square trail
OL,6,FThe first adaptation, Bridget Jones's
OL,7,FDiary, was released in April 2001 and
OL,8,Fbecame a global hit, earning Zellweger
OL,9,Fher first Oscar nomination.
OL,11,FThe statue shows Zellweger's character
OL,12,Fclutching her diary, and was the first
OL,13,Ffigure to honour a romantic comedy in
OL,14,Fthe square.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/6
