OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1776423773
OL,3,CBridget Jones statue becomes permanent
OL,4,Cfixture on Leicester Square trail
OL,6,FThe film series began life as an
OL,7,Fanonymous column called Bridget
OL,8,FJones's Diary in The Independent
OL,9,Fnewspaper in 1995, written by Helen
OL,10,FFielding, intended to appear as an
OL,11,Factual personal diary of a single
OL,12,Fwoman in her 30s. It spawned four
OL,13,Fnovels.
OL,15,FBridget Jones's Diary (2001), Bridget
OL,16,FJones: The Edge of Reason (2004),
OL,17,FBridget Jones's Baby (2016), and
OL,18,FBridget Jones: Mad About the Boy have
OL,19,Fearned 900 million dollars worldwide.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/6
