OL,3,CBridget Jones statue becomes permanent
OL,4,Cfixture on Leicester Square trail
OL,6,FThe Scenes in the Square trail
OL,7,Flaunched in 2020and is home to 10
OL,8,Fpermanent statues, and regular new
OL,9,Fadditions of temporary statues.
OL,11,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,12,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,13,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,14,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,15,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,16,Fbelow...
